          "orderIndex": 0,
          "blockType": "rich_text",
          "title": null,
          "data": {
            "html": "<p>Sarita's experiences are not individualized in nature and is the norm as opposed to the exception for people with SCD. Malina partners with Sarita to meet her where she's at and to advocate for her needs without any judgement. Listen to Malina's final reflections and consider how you would help Sarita if this were you in this situation.</p>"
